        <title>Update Google Analytics to GA4</title>
        <link>http://localhost:1313/hugo/hugo-add-google-analytics/</link>
        <pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        <author>li3huo (li3huo)</author>
        <guid>http://localhost:1313/hugo/hugo-add-google-analytics/</guid>
        <description>
            &lt;p&gt;在官网找到 Google Analytics 4 Property Setup Assistant, 点击确认后出现 &lt;code&gt;You have successfully connected your properties.&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://support.google.com/analytics/answer/9744165?hl=en_US&amp;amp;utm_id=ad&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Learn more about Google Analytics 4 properties&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hugo 后台告警&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;WARN  Google Analytics &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;GA4&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; replaced Google Universal Analytics &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;UA&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; effective &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; July 2023. See https://support.google.com/analytics/answer/11583528. Create a GA4 property and data stream, &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;then&lt;/span&gt; replace the Google Analytics ID in your site configuration with the new value.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;修改 &lt;code&gt;hugo.yml&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-yaml&#34; data-lang=&#34;yaml&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;googleAnalytics&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;w&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;88888888&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;w&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;生效后，页面中加入了&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-html&#34; data-lang=&#34;html&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;script&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;async&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;src&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=88888888&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;script&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
